                            <comment id="13485075" author="stack" created="Fri, 26 Oct 2012 17:55:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Chatting w/ Elliott more on this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;+ sequence id should probably be in .META.&lt;br/&gt;
+ having some metrics history would be sweet.  We could let it TTL out after an hour so we didn&apos;t keep too much around (or after an hour do the TSDB rollups if wanted)&lt;br/&gt;
+ A TSDB like query page for looking at the cluster over time would be sweet.&lt;br/&gt;
+ We should be careful to ensure we do not repeat the mistakes of the distant past when we used to keep a region history table into which we noted region transition; the problem there was our trying to record events like close when say, the cluster was going down, and the table we were trying to write would be down &amp;#8211; the writer could hang&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This seems like a small thing to do that could improve usability alot.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13485077" author="stack" created="Fri, 26 Oct 2012 17:56:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Upping priority since seems like small change w/ big payoff.  Making it noob for now in case someone wants to pick it up meantime.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
